These test require the following:

Node needs to be installed, nodejs.org.  This ensures that npm is working.

Mocha needs to be installed globally:

npm install -g mocha

Package.json needs to initialised

npm init

Chai and JsDom need to be installed in development mode

npm install --save-dev chai jsdom

A test folder needs to be created and the two files private.js and setup.js copied
to the folder

The test are run using:

npm test

To run the test in continuous mode use the following (not )

npm run watch
